    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/a23bb87cf7e23792ac5edbcba860474f.avif?t=1750427183\" width=620 height=277 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >手写的怀旧</h2>回到90年代，通过精美的手绘信件，追随萨拉的生活诡计。了解更多关于她的朋友，她书呆子般的执念，或者为什么她有个最烦人的妹妹。<br><br>然后随着莎拉年龄的增长，一切开始数字化。陶醉于21世纪初互联网的怀旧像素世界，同时感受青春期的那些故事，焦虑和乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/77038c1ebb4d113ccd3129212ae1ca77.poster.avif?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/77038c1ebb4d113ccd3129212ae1ca77.webm?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/77038c1ebb4d113ccd3129212ae1ca77.mp4?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/e3b48abc6644cf9f416807b7f1394a1d.webp?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=5 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改变你的未来</h2>看着萨拉长大，并做出会改变她今后生活的决定（不要有压力）。报复你的妹妹，整天玩游戏或者坠入爱河。这一切都由你决定。<br><br>不喜欢结局？那就继续去重写她的故事。（看见没？我们说过，不要有压力。）<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/de604de3f51ede9d513620d5a1c32653.poster.avif?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/de604de3f51ede9d513620d5a1c32653.webm?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/de604de3f51ede9d513620d5a1c32653.mp4?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/e3b48abc6644cf9f416807b7f1394a1d.webp?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=5 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >文字的力量</h2>在一个由纸和电脑组成的世界里，文字很重要。所以，用它们来改变阻挡你的图画，帮助友善的角色们，并与莎拉的朋友互动吧。<br><br>有时会很难找到合适的文字。尤其是对像莎拉这样害羞的人而言。所以请帮她把它们拆开，创造新的文字给她用吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/0782e0293fdba1bbb0e3d0e552b9a915.poster.avif?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/0782e0293fdba1bbb0e3d0e552b9a915.webm?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/0782e0293fdba1bbb0e3d0e552b9a915.mp4?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/e3b48abc6644cf9f416807b7f1394a1d.webp?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=5 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满趣味，有益身心</h2>Letters是一个关于友情、成长和找寻生活方式的温馨、时常有趣也偶尔悲伤的故事。探索萨拉丰富多彩的世界，并用文字的力量去改变她的人生！<br><br>或者……就堆堆猫咪什么的也行。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/b40b3bf6727e571cdce69b2cb90f4f98.poster.avif?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/b40b3bf6727e571cdce69b2cb90f4f98.webm?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/b40b3bf6727e571cdce69b2cb90f4f98.mp4?t=1750427183\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1033080/extras/e3b48abc6644cf9f416807b7f1394a1d.webp?t=1750427183\" width=616 height=5 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你从未见过的，基于文字的创新谜语机制</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>灵感源自现实生活，引发共鸣的成长故事</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>众多分支故事线，每一次玩都能让你探索新的可能</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>伴随萨拉年龄的成长，感受精美的手绘视觉和像素艺术</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>温馨、有趣且休闲的游戏，注重叙述，享受文字的乐趣</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>有助于在快乐中练习英语</li></ul>",
